name: Side Effects
description:
This piece of art is the collaboration of Size Music TH x Bright Me To The Moon

This is my first motion collage artwork which is inspired from the story of the collage creator "Bright Me To The Moon".  She tried happily and excitedly to describe and put her feeling at that moment and her side effects into this piece. 

The collage creator's additional story of this artwork will be posted on her Twitter, that is linked on the H=N account, after be minted this work a few days.

Hope you love this!
Have a great time!

love,
